`$HORIZON_SYSTEM/logs/`, or any other brain's folder. Attempting to access these
paths will fail at the OS level regardless of instructions.

## Skills

Your skills live at `~/.claude/skills` — which AIOS links to the shared
`skills_bin` skill tier (read+execute for all brains). Before searching for a
skill, **check `skills_bin/index.md` first** for what's available. You cannot
see `skills_sbin` (the owner-only tier); that is by design.

